BVApp.models.Data["reviews/en/la-mano-verde.html"] ="La Mano Verde is a purely vegan gourmet restau&shy;rant. Accord&shy;ingly, the prices are some&shy;what higher. <br/><br/>Go on a fasci&shy;nat&shy;ing culi&shy;nary expe&shy;di&shy;tion along the excit&shy;ing menu in a cosy atmo&shy;sphere. Even long-​time vegans are amazed all over again by these inter&shy;est&shy;ing compo&shy;si&shy;tions. As a special&shy;ity, a number of the dishes are served as raw vege&shy;tar&shy;ian food. <br/><br/>In 2009 La Mano Verde received PETAs Proggy Award granted to the best vegan restau&shy;rant.<br/><br/>";
