BVApp.models.Data["reviews/en/kaufland.html"] ="<h3>Dairy alter&shy;na&shy;tives</h3><ul><li>soya yogurt, soya milk, soya cook&shy;ing cream (Alpro brand)</li><li>Soya&shy;too brand alter&shy;na&shy;tive to whipped cream</li><li>Alsan brand margarine</li></ul><h3>ice cream</h3><ul><li>Cristallo Big Choc Soya\" (lolly), 3x120 ml for €1.99</li><li>Swedish Glace Milk&shy;free\" Magnum-​style lolly</li><li>Swedish Glace\" choco&shy;late or rasp&shy;berry flavour, 750 ml for €2.59 </li><li>lemon sorbet in the zest of a lemon </li><li>rasp&shy;berry smoothie-​style ice lolly </li><li>Nimm2-​Eis\" (ice pop with stick) </li><li>Nasch-​Eisspezial&shy;itäten\" (vanilla or straw&shy;berry flavour)</li></ul>";
BVApp.models.Data["reviews/en/cafe-rosenduft.html"] ="In 2004, Berlin's first certi&shy;fied organic café opened near the S-​Bahn station Lichter&shy;felde Ost. The café is fully vege&shy;tar&shy;ian provided that you are will&shy;ing to over&shy;look that they sell dead fish in the form of salmon tart once every four weeks.<br/><br/>Theres plenty for vegans, too: There is a soy milk option for the coffee special&shy;i&shy;ties, unfor&shy;tu&shy;nately at an extra charge. They usually offer two vegan cakes (pear-​walnut and coco-​ tanger&shy;ine) and in the summer&shy;time, the five vegan flavours of ice cream (soy-​coconut, straw&shy;berry, lemon, buck&shy;thorn berry, fruits of forest) will satisfy not just a vegans sweet tooth. The vegan options for savoury dishes are: salad with home&shy;made Ital&shy;ian dress&shy;ing, tomato soup and red lentil soup. They serve a great vegan break&shy;fast as well. The deli&shy;cious organic spelt rolls and bread can be enjoyed with vegan soy margarine or cold fake meats, for instance.<br/><br/>Having room for just about ten people, the café is rela&shy;tively small, but in warm weather you can sit outside as well. Inside, there is a play corner for chil&shy;dren. The toilet is wheelchair acces&shy;si&shy;ble, which consti&shy;tutes a notable excep&shy;tion among the restau&shy;rants listed here. Smok&shy;ing is strictly prohib&shy;ited at Café Rosenduft, even outside.<br/><br/>";
