BVApp.models.Data["reviews/de/india-palace.html"] ="Direkt an der Herm&shy;ann&shy;str&shy;aße in Neukö&shy;lln befi&shy;n&shy;det sich der India Palace 2. Hier steht der Chef selber am Herd. Das Gesc&shy;häft ist zwar nicht spezi&shy;ell vegan ausge&shy;wi&shy;e&shy;sen, doch ist die Zuber&shy;ei&shy;tung veganer Spei&shy;sen für den freund&shy;li&shy;c&shy;hen Inhaber nichts Unge&shy;wö&shy;h&shy;n&shy;li&shy;c&shy;hes. Die Grundk&shy;o&shy;m&shy;po&shy;nen&shy;ten aller Geri&shy;c&shy;hte werden nach dessen Angaben ohnehin ohne Zugabe tieri&shy;sc&shy;her Ingre&shy;d&shy;en&shy;zien zuber&shy;ei&shy;tet. Diese werden in der Regel erst später hinzug&shy;eg&shy;e&shy;ben.<br/><br/>Alle vege&shy;taris&shy;c&shy;hen Geri&shy;c&shy;hte können auch vegan zuber&shy;ei&shy;tet werden, wenn es gewüns&shy;cht wird.<br/><br/>Die Geri&shy;c&shy;hte liegen zwis&shy;c&shy;hen 2 und 7,50 , sind also für ziem&shy;lich jeden ersc&shy;hwi&shy;ng&shy;lich. Zudem bietet die Location einen Liefer&shy;se&shy;r&shy;vice mit einem Mind&shy;e&shy;stbe&shy;ste&shy;ll&shy;w&shy;ert von 15  an.<br/><br/>";
BVApp.models.Data["reviews/en/dolores-burritos.html"] ="This small restau&shy;rant is situ&shy;ated near Alexan&shy;der&shy;platz (square) at Rosa-​Luxem&shy;burg Straße 7. The dishes are as wild and loud as the music and the uncon&shy;ven&shy;tional décor. The restau&shy;rant special&shy;izes in Burri&shy;tos and, thanks to the grow&shy;ing trend towards the vegan diet, offers a vegan option as well. The vegan options are clearly marked.<br/><br/>The staff told us that they are very care&shy;ful to use only &amp;quot;vegan&amp;quot; kitchen appli&shy;ances and cutlery (e. g. deep fryers and knives) when prepar&shy;ing vegan dishes. If you would like, you can make sure of this your&shy;self as patrons can see the kitchen area and watch the staff prepare the food.<br/><br/>The staff is friendly, constantly scur&shy;ries around and seems to have every&shy;thing under control even though the restau&shy;rant occa&shy;sion&shy;ally has an air of chaos to it.<br/><br/>The reason&shy;able prices allow for a second burrito in case youre famished. The home&shy;made lemon&shy;ades are another special&shy;ity and if you have a sweet tooth, you will be happy to know that Dolores also offers vegan cakes from Freck&shy;les.<br/><br/>";
